OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start with some spots of
OL,6,Frain towards the northeast, otherwise
OL,7,Fa bright morning with sunny spells.
OL,8,FSome showers developing by the
OL,9,Fafternoon, especially in the east,
OL,10,Fwith a few heavy and possibly thundery
OL,11,Fshowers developing. Feeling warmer.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers fading this evening,
OL,14,Fleaving a dry and clear night to
OL,15,Fdevelop across much of the region.
OL,16,FHowever, showers may continue
OL,17,Fovernight in western Cornwall. Turning
OL,18,Fchilly in the countryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
