OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRather cloudy at times
OL,6,Facross southern coasts with some
OL,7,Ffurther showery rain towards Cornwall
OL,8,Fand possibly later into Devon. Largely
OL,9,Fdry with sunny spells elsewhere, and
OL,10,Ffeeling warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,13,Frain clearing Sunday with a dry but
OL,14,Fcooler afternoon following. Largely
OL,15,Fdry but cool on Monday and Tuesday,
OL,16,Fwith some bright spells, but rain
OL,17,Fpossible overnight into Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
